                "invention-title": [
                    "Device and method for preparing combustible gas through continuous pyrolysis of biomass",
                    "一种用于生物质连续热解制备可燃气的装置及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a device and method for preparing combustible gas through continuous pyrolysis of biomass. The device comprises a feeding unit capable of controlling the oxygen content in materials, a pyrolysis unit capable of adjusting the retention time of the materials, and a catalytic conversion unit for circulating a liquid-phase product. The feeding unit capable of controlling the oxygen content in materials comprises a nitrogen storage tank, a nitrogen flow meter, a stock bin, a feeding groove, a radar level gage, a cyclone separator and an oxygen detector. The pyrolysis unit capable of adjusting the retention time of the materials comprises a pyrolysis reactor capable of adjusting an inclination angle, a nitrogen flow meter, a pyrolysis heating furnace, a hydraulic support, a radar level gauge and a solid carbon collecting tank; the catalytic conversion unit for liquid-phase product circulation comprises a hydrogen storage tank, a hydrogen flow meter, a catalytic conversion reactor, a catalytic conversion heating furnace, a cooler, a gas-liquid separator and the like. According to the invention, continuous and efficient pyrolysis of the biomass can be realized, the biomass is converted into combustible gas, and the problems of difficult continuous production, low combustible gas content and low calorific value of the traditional pyrolysis technology are solved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种用于生物质连续热解制备可燃气的装置及方法，包括可控制物料中氧气含量的进料单元、可调节物料停留时间的热解单元、液相产物循环的催化转化单元；可控制物料中氧气含量的进料单元包括氮气储罐、氮气流量计、料仓、进料槽、雷达料位计、旋风分离器、氧气检测器；可调节物料停留时间的热解单元包括可调节倾斜角度的热解反应器、氮气流量计、热解加热炉、液压支撑器、雷达料位计、固体炭收集槽；液相产物循环的催化转化单元包括氢气储罐、氢气流量计、催化转化反应器、催化转化加热炉、冷却器、气液分离器等。本发明能实现生物质连续高效热解，将生物质转化为可燃气，克服了传统热解技术连续生产困难、可燃气含量少、热值低的问题。"
                }
